description: Twelve residents of Abbotswood Nursing Home have now died with Covid-19, the health minister says.
title: Coronavirus: Six more deaths at Abbotswood Nursing Home
title_page: Coronavirus: Six more deaths at Abbotswood Nursing Home - BBC News
maintext: He said some residents had been moved to the Newlands building on the Noble's Hospital site while parts of the care home were deep-cleaned, but would be "transferred back" once the work was complete.
